      "section_kind": "weather_opening",
      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 10.0,
      "text": "It is currently a clear morning in Berlin-Tempelhof with a temperature of 26 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 19.131,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 15.707,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a7b6fcc848c"
      ],
      "end": 41.197,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3",
        "s4"
      ],
      "start": 19.131,
      "text": "NVIDIA and Amazon Web Services are expanding their collaboration to move production scale AI into the real world. The launch of Amazon EC2 G7 instances using Blackwell GPUs provides up to four point six times the inference performance of previous models. To improve semantic search, NVIDIA cuVS library vector indexing is now the default for Amazon OpenSearch Serverless."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "ac88ac76c06"
      ],
      "end": 59.458,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s5",
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 41.197,
      "text": "This push for scale faces a physical bottleneck in power consumption. Power costs can account for forty percent of the total operating expenses for an AI factory. NVIDIA is now focusing on full stack optimizations to maximize performance per watt and lower the cost of every token generated."
    },
    {
      "end": 62.121,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 59.458,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 66.687,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 62.121,
      "text": "This afternoon will remain clear with temperatures between 28 and 33 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 69.73,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 66.687,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 75.817,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 69.73,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 85.709,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s12"
      ],
      "start": 75.817,
      "text": "[very very long pause before speaking; then mature adult voice, most emotional, strong, warm, radiant, deeply encouraging; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    }
  ],
